# Business skill routing

Curated set only (~44 skills). Full list: [skills-manifest.json](../../skills-manifest.json).

| User intent | Skill |
|-------------|-------|
| Find leads / prospect list | `lead-research-assistant` |
| Industry overview | `analyze-industry` |
| Company business deep-dive | `company-research` |
| Company tech stack / engineering | `company-technical-research` |
| ICP / ideal customer | `ideal-customer-profile` |
| GTM plan / launch | `gtm-strategy`, `beachhead-segment`, `gtm-motions` |
| Competitive sales deck | `competitive-battlecard`, `competitor-analysis` |
| Positioning / messaging | `positioning-ideas`, `value-prop-statements`, `value-proposition` |
| PRD / specs | `create-prd` |
| Discovery / assumptions | `brainstorm-ideas-new`, `identify-assumptions-new`, `prioritize-assumptions` |
| Strategy canvas | `lean-canvas`, `product-strategy` |
| Pricing | `pricing-strategy`, `monetization-strategy` |
| Metrics | `north-star-metric`, `metrics-dashboard`, `ab-test-analysis` |
| User research | `interview-script`, `summarize-interview`, `user-personas` |
| Direct-response ad copy, hooks, captions, landing page copy | `direct-response-copy-engine` |
| Audit ad copy / pressure-test draft | `direct-response-copy-engine` (Audit mode) |
| Short-form video script / carousel ad copy | `direct-response-copy-engine` |
| Map knowledge from docs/files | `graphify` |

Optional skills (not pre-installed): run `scripts/install-optional-skill.ps1 -Name linkedin-content` etc.
